<lb n="3" break="no"/>hō varadanāmātyacciraṁ bhūtalē jīyātpeddanamaṁtrivaryyatanayassa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁgītaratnākaraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śākē<unclear>bdē</unclear> nagaratnabhānugaṇitē pakṣē sitē kārttikē saptamyā
